## 4. Context Pipeline (8-Layer Architecture)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph "User Message Input"
        UM["User Message"]
    end

    subgraph "8-Layer Context Assembly"
        L0["L0: Identity Core<br/>(~300 tokens)"]
        L1["L1: Global Preferences<br/>(~500 tokens)"]
        L2["L2: Topic Context<br/>(~1,500 tokens)"]
        L3["L3: Entity Context<br/>(~1,000 tokens)"]
        L4["L4: Conversation Arc<br/>(~2,000 tokens)"]
        L5["L5: JIT Retrieval<br/>(~2,500 tokens)"]
        L6["L6: Message History<br/>(~3,500 tokens)"]
        L7["L7: User Message<br/>(Variable)"]
    end

    subgraph "Pipeline Stages"
        Detect["Context Detection"]
        Embed["Embedding Generation"]
        Bundle["Bundle Compilation"]
        Budget["Token Budget Calculation"]
        Assemble["Prompt Assembly"]
    end

    UM --> Detect
    Detect --> Embed
    
    subgraph "Parallel Fetch Stage"
        PF[("Parallel Fetch")]
    end
    
    Embed --> PF
    PF --> L0
    PF --> L1
    
    subgraph "Bundle Compilation"
        BC[("Bundle Compiler")]
    end
    
    BC --> L2
    BC --> L3
    BC --> L4
    BC --> L5
    
    L0 --> Budget
    L1 --> Budget
    L2 --> Budget
    L3 --> Budget
    L4 --> Budget
    L5 --> Budget
    
    Budget --> Assemble
    
    L6 --> Assemble
    L7 --> Assemble
    
    subgraph "Output"
        LLM["LLM Prompt"]
    end
    
    Assemble --> LLM
```

