## Summary

This visualization document covers:

1. **Project Structure** - Monorepo with frontend, backend, and shared packages
2. **System Architecture** - Full stack with Next.js, Express, PostgreSQL
3. **Database Schema** - Key models for users, conversations, ACUs, memories
4. **Context Pipeline** - 8-layer parallel assembly with streaming support
5. **API Routes** - All backend endpoints and middleware
6. **Frontend Components** - Pages, UI components, hooks, libraries
7. **Memory System** - ACU architecture with 9 memory types
8. **Security & Auth** - Virtual users, JWT, Zero-Knowledge encryption
9. **Data Flow** - Event-driven architecture with workers
10. **Rights Layer & Sentinel** - 6-tier ownership and 13 detection algorithms